# work-line
- My shift at @work-area starts in @time-until. I should probably get moving.
- I've spent all day recalibrating @equipment. It still says everything is fine.
- Someone left @cargo right outside @work-area. Again.
- The supervisor says we're @schedule-status. The supervisor is lying.
- I swapped shifts with @coworker. I think I got the worse end of the deal.
- They gave me a new access badge. It opens every door except the one to my workplace.

