# station-life-line
- The lights near @station-area have been flickering since @time-reference. Nobody seems worried.
- One of the lifts is making @odd-sound again. I'd take the stairs, if we had any.
- They say the air recyclers are running normally. They always say that.
- The observation deck is quiet @quiet-time. It's a good place to think.
- I took a wrong turn near @busy-area and ended up in @remote-area. All these corridors look the same.
- The station announcement has repeated the same apology @repeat-count. I wonder what happened.

