- before the morning rush
- during the artificial night
- when no cruise ships are docked
- around the middle of second shift
- just after the lights dim

# repeat-count
- four times
- every hour today
- since breakfast
- for the last twenty minutes
- often enough that I've memorised it

# travel-line
- The shuttle from @origin was held up by @delay-chain. At least the seats were warm.
- If you're travelling to @destination, bring your own food. That's all I'll say.
- My connection leaves from docking ring @ring-number, assuming they haven't moved it again.
- The ticket said “direct service.” Apparently stopping at @destination still counts as direct.
- I miss ships with windows. A camera feed is not the same thing.

# delay-chain
- [6] @delay-reason
- [1] @delay-reason, then @delay-chain

